<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><!DOCTYPE paragraph PUBLIC "-//IFRS//DTD DITA Paragraph//EN" "../../../DocTypes/com.ifrs.doctype/dtd/paragraph.dtd"><paragraph base="F31714636" id="IFRS15_100"><paranum class="- topic/title paragraph/paranum "/><titlealts><navtitle>100</navtitle></titlealts><prolog><data name="standard_number" value="IFRS 15"/><data name="paranum" value="100"/></prolog><body><p id="IFRS15_P0406">An entity shall update the amortisation to reflect a significant change in the entity’s expected timing of transfer to the <xref base="F31716738" href="IFRS15_APPA.dita#IFRS15_APPA/IFRS15_DI0004" scope="local">customer<ph outputclass="def_xref"><xref keyref="GLOSSARY_customer"/></ph></xref> of the goods or services to which the asset relates. Such a change shall be accounted for as a change in accounting estimate in accordance with <xref base="F35271316" href="../ias08/IAS08_TOC.dita#IAS08_TOC0001" id="IFRS15_X0486">IAS 8</xref>.</p></body></paragraph>